# This file pins the prebuilt PDFium release that JPDFium's publish workflows
# consume instead of building PDFium from source on every push.
#
# The value must be the tag of a GitHub Release in this repository that was
# produced by the `Prebuild PDFium` workflow (.github/workflows/prebuild-pdfium.yml).
# That release carries one tarball per platform: pdfium-<platform>.tar.gz.
#
# Format: pdfium-YYYYMMDD-<shortSha>
# Example: pdfium-20260420-65816fe
#
# Bootstrap: if this file is empty (as on first install), trigger the
# `Prebuild PDFium` workflow manually. It will build PDFium ×5, publish a
# release, and open a PR bumping this file to the new tag.
#
# Subsequent updates: the weekly cron in `Prebuild PDFium` auto-opens a PR
# bumping this pin when EmbedPDF's fork HEAD moves. Review release notes and
# merge when you want the new version to take effect.
